{"tid":1018192,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"瑞和街掃黃 警方入境拘十二名內地女","createTime":"2019-02-12T05:19:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-29T10:26:04.000Z","uid":170044,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"59c8d2604d46344a407d49ebbd08cf6b269f4817","tid":1018192,"uid":170044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T05:19:08.000Z","msg":"今日（11日）中午，觀塘警區及秀茂坪警區特別職務隊聯同入境事務處人員，進行代號「孤影」及「萬里達」的掃黃行動，突擊搜查通明街、宜安街、康寧道、崇仁街、輔仁街、瑞和街、物華街及觀塘工業區一帶，拘捕共12名年齡介乎23至45歲持雙程證的內地女子，涉嫌違反逗留條件。所有被捕女子正被扣留調查，稍後將交由入境事務處跟進。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2r4DdnF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2r4DdnF.png&h=6ad2a750&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"77234054f91d3c845b220b4b7be2ba3c480e021d","tid":1018192,"uid":2040,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T05:21:59.000Z","msg":"瑞和街=葛咸城"},{"pid":"980cf313a229f37599c39a118c09e61ca2d9e6af","tid":1018192,"uid":170044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"77234054f91d3c845b220b4b7be2ba3c480e021d","tid":1018192,"uid":2040,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T05:21:59.000Z","msg":"瑞和街=葛咸城"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T05:23:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/C2b2nFKdI18\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FC2b2nFKdI18&d=DoGI4G7aG2aFCjNgNSWIuiukga04qSQtFIF%2FU0RrEoA%3D&h=a9f5cbef\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/C2b2nFKdI18</a>"},{"pid":"5d94067efe6c1d23aecf8c98ceb1bc812752b93a","tid":1018192,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T05:51:22.000Z","msg":"樓主唔係撐世？"},{"pid":"00618606257fb2f7150cae2c3b7d22ea893ddfe0","tid":1018192,"uid":170044,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5d94067efe6c1d23aecf8c98ceb1bc812752b93a","tid":1018192,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T05:51:22.000Z","msg":"樓主唔係撐世？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T06:44:54.000Z","msg":"唔撐笠水狗"},{"pid":"4d4